  "Description": {
    "English": "This grand hood is worn by the upper ranks of Gek at events and conventions, distinguishing the esteemed Trade Lord from the lowly Hireling.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit with this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Appearance Override</span> at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "吉克的上流阶层人士在出席活动和会议时会穿戴这款高贵的兜帽，从而区分尊贵的贸易领主与低贱的雇工。<br><br>使用这款专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">外观覆盖</span>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>改变你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "吉客族上流社會在活動或集會時所穿的豪華斗篷，與尊貴商王和低階受雇員的服裝有明顯區別。<br><br>這個特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">外觀覆寫</span>能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>中改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
